Steps.Text: Wait 30 seconds, then pull to BYPASS
PRIM GLY EVAP OUT TEMP ind - 38-43F
Monitor on MDC-2: Fill until 50% reached.
Monitor GLY PRIM OUT and IN TEMP for 5 min.
Outlet temp > than inlet temp after 5 min then PRIM GLY TO RAD bypass, retry in 10 minutes.
P-602: REPRESS O2 PRESS ind > 865 psia
